<a id="nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces"></a>
### Nested Schema for `mgmt_inband_interfaces`

Required:

- `interface_name` (String) Configure a specific interface

Optional:

- `allow_all` (Boolean) All Protocols
- `allow_all_ipv4_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--allow_all_ipv4_hosts))
- `allow_all_ipv4_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--allow_all_ipv4_prefixes))
- `allow_all_ipv6_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--allow_all_ipv6_hosts))
- `allow_all_ipv6_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--allow_all_ipv6_prefixes))
- `http` (Boolean) HTTP(S)
- `http_ipv4_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--http_ipv4_hosts))
- `http_ipv4_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--http_ipv4_prefixes))
- `netconf` (Boolean) NETCONF version 1.1 protocol
- `netconf_ipv4_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--netconf_ipv4_hosts))
- `netconf_ipv4_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--netconf_ipv4_prefixes))
- `netconf_ipv6_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--netconf_ipv6_hosts))
- `netconf_ipv6_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--netconf_ipv6_prefixes))
- `snmp` (Boolean) SNMP (all versions)
- `snmp_ipv4_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--snmp_ipv4_hosts))
- `snmp_ipv4_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--snmp_ipv4_prefixes))
- `snmp_ipv6_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--snmp_ipv6_hosts))
- `snmp_ipv6_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--snmp_ipv6_prefixes))
- `ssh` (Boolean) Secure Shell (v1 & v2)
- `ssh_ipv4_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--ssh_ipv4_hosts))
- `ssh_ipv4_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--ssh_ipv4_prefixes))
- `ssh_ipv6_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--ssh_ipv6_hosts))
- `ssh_ipv6_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--ssh_ipv6_prefixes))
- `telnet` (Boolean) Telnet
- `telnet_ipv4_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--telnet_ipv4_hosts))
- `telnet_ipv4_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--telnet_ipv4_prefixes))
- `telnet_ipv6_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--telnet_ipv6_hosts))
- `telnet_ipv6_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--telnet_ipv6_prefixes))
- `tftp` (Boolean) TFTP
- `tftp_ipv4_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--tftp_ipv4_hosts))
- `tftp_ipv4_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--tftp_ipv4_prefixes))
- `tftp_ipv6_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--tftp_ipv6_hosts))
- `tftp_ipv6_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--tftp_ipv6_prefixes))
- `xml` (Boolean) XML
- `xml_ipv4_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--xml_ipv4_hosts))
- `xml_ipv4_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--xml_ipv4_prefixes))
- `xml_ipv6_hosts` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--xml_ipv6_hosts))
- `xml_ipv6_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv6 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_inband_interfaces--xml_ipv6_prefixes))

- `http_ipv4_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_oob_interfaces--http_ipv4_prefixes))

- `telnet_ipv4_prefixes` (Attributes List) Enter IPv4 address with prefix (see [below for nested schema](#nestedatt--mgmt_oob_interfaces--telnet_ipv4_prefixes))

## Import

Import is supported using the following syntax:

The [`terraform import` command](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/cli/commands/import) can be used, for example:

```shell
terraform import iosxr_control_plane.example ""
```
